skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-8-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-8-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-8-150x225.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"callout-box-block_843bce74bd4d511fdaecc1b12114d405\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e What You’ll Need\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eChia pudding and chocolate-covered strawberries combine to create an indulgent yet light dessert. \u003cstrong\u003eSee the exact measurements in the recipe card below.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1.jpg\" alt=\"Chocolate Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" data-pin-description=\"If you like chia seed pudding, you will love this Chocolate-Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding. It is a healthy dessert loaded with 25 grams of fiber! #chia #chiaseeds #chiapudding #healthysnack #highfiber #healthydessert #valentinesday\" data-pin-title=\"Chocolate Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1.jpg 1200w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-1-150x225.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMilk:\u003c/strong\u003e Use whichever milk you prefer. I have tried it with almond milk, coconut milk, and a blend of the two (I like \u003ca href=\"https://www.califiafarms.com/products/toasted-coconut-almondmilk-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow external\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eCalifia Farms Coconut \u0026amp; Almond Milk\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eStrawberries:\u003c/strong\u003e Fresh and freeze-dried strawberries provide sweetness and fiber.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMaple Syrup:\u003c/strong\u003e I love \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Wholesome-Yum-Keto-Maple-Syrup/dp/B08ML7DHPH?th=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener sponsored external\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eWholesome Yum sugar-free maple syrup\u003c/a\u003e, but any kind will work.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eChia Seeds\u003c/strong\u003e plump up when they soak in milk, creating a high-fiber pudding. They’re also packed with omega-3s and antioxidants.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eChocolate Chips:\u003c/strong\u003e You’ll need semi-sweet chocolate chips to melt on top of each ramekin. \u003ca href=\"https://www.lilys.com/products/lilys-semi-sweet-style-baking-chips-9-oz-bag.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow external\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eLily’s chocolate chips\u003c/a\u003e are a great sugar-free option.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eCoconut Oil: \u003c/strong\u003eMelt coconut oil with chocolate chips to create a hard “magic shell” topping.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eHow to Make Strawberry Chia Pudding\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis easy strawberry chia pudding is great to make ahead, so it’s ready whenever a chocolate craving hits! \u003cstrong\u003eSee the printable instructions are below in the recipe card.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" data-id=\"141360\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-550x825.jpg\" alt=\"Blend strawberries and milk.\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2-150x225.jpg 150w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-2.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eBlend strawberries and milk.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" data-id=\"141361\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-550x825.jpg\" alt=\"Add chia seeds\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3-150x225.jpg 150w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-3.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eAdd chia seeds\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" data-id=\"141355\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-550x825.jpg\" alt=\"Mix and let it sit until the seeds expand.\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5-150x225.jpg 150w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-5.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eMix and let it sit until the seeds expand.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMake the Chia Pudding:\u003c/strong\u003e Blend milk, fresh and freeze-dried strawberries, and syrup in a blender until smooth. Transfer to a large bowl and stir in the chia seeds until there are no clumps. Let it sit for 15 minutes while the seeds expand.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRefrigerate the Pudding:\u003c/strong\u003e Put a quarter cup of strawberries into 5 ramekins, and pour chia pudding on top. Refrigerate the pudding for at least an hour until firm.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMake the Chocolate Topping: \u003c/strong\u003eMelt the chocolate and coconut oil in a small bowl in the microwave. Alternatively, you can set up a double broiler by boiling water in a small saucepan. Then, place a glass bowl filled with chocolate and oil over the water and stir until melted.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Serve:\u003c/strong\u003e Pour the chocolate on top of each ramekin or \u003ca href=\"https://bit.ly/3VcVwXG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow external\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e7-ounce glass\u003c/a\u003e and garnish with extra strawberries. Refrigerate for an hour or 2 until the chocolate hardens.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" data-pin-description=\"If you like chia seed pudding, you will love this Chocolate-Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding. It is a healthy dessert loaded with 25 grams of fiber! #chia #chiaseeds #chiapudding #healthysnack #highfiber #healthydessert\" data-pin-title=\"Chocolate Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6.jpg\" alt=\"Melted Chocolate\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6.jpg 1200w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-500x750.jpg 500w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-550x825.jpg 550w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-170x255.jpg 170w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-600x900.jpg 600w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-260x390.jpg 260w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-6-150x225.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eVariations\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBerries: \u003c/strong\u003eSubstitute raspberries with strawberries.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSweetener: \u003c/strong\u003eSwap maple syrup for honey or agave.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSkip the Oil\u003c/strong\u003e if you prefer. It will make the chocolate harder, so make sure to spread a thinner layer over the top so it’s easier to break through with a spoon.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eStorage\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eChia pudding lasts 4 days in the refrigerator, making it excellent for meal prep.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1800\" data-pin-description=\"If you like chia seed pudding, you will love this Chocolate-Covered Strawberry Chia Pudding. It is a healthy dessert loaded with 25 grams of fiber! #chia #chiaseeds #chiapudding #healthysnack #highfiber #healthydessert\" data-pin-title=\"Strawberry Chia Pudding\" src=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-7.jpg\" alt=\"Strawberry Chia Pudding\" srcset=\"https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-7.jpg 1200w, https://www.skinnytaste.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Chocolate-Covered-Strawberry-Chia-Pudding-7-500x750.jpg 500w